      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{{ 'ariya-ingredients.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}\n\n<div class=\"ariya-ingredients\">\n  <div class=\"ariya-ing-container\">\n\n    <div class=\"ariya-ing-hero\">\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-hero__label\">Calm Nights Formula</p>\n      <h1 class=\"ariya-ing-hero__heading\">What's Inside &mdash; And Why</h1>\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-hero__sub\">Every ingredient is here for a reason. No fillers, no proprietary blends. Just the compounds that work &mdash; at doses that matter.</p>\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-hero__badge-row\">\n        <span class=\"ariya-ing-hero__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> 7 Ingredients</span>\n        <span class=\"ariya-ing-hero__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Fully Dosed</span>\n        <span class=\"ariya-ing-hero__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> No Proprietary Blends</span>\n        <span class=\"ariya-ing-hero__badge\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> No Melatonin</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"ariya-ing-list\">\n\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-card\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__number\" data-name=\"L-Tryptophan\"></div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"ariya-ing-card__name\">L-Tryptophan</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__spec\">USP-grade &bull; &ge;98% purity &bull; Fermentation-derived</span>\n          <p class=\"ariya-ing-card__purpose\">Supports the body's natural serotonin and melatonin pathways involved in sleep regulation.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-wrap\">\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage\">690</span>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-unit\">mg</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-card\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__number\" data-name=\"L-Theanine\"></div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"ariya-ing-card__name\">L-Theanine</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__spec\">High-purity amino acid</span>\n          <p class=\"ariya-ing-card__purpose\">Promotes relaxation and supports a calm mental state without causing next-day grogginess.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-wrap\">\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage\">250</span>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-unit\">mg</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-card\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__number\" data-name=\"Lemon Balm\"></div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"ariya-ing-card__name\">Lemon Balm Extract 5:1</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__spec\">&ge;2.5% rosmarinic acid</span>\n          <p class=\"ariya-ing-card__purpose\">Helps reduce stress and supports sleep quality. The active compound, rosmarinic acid, is verified in every batch.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-wrap\">\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage\">175</span>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-unit\">mg</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-card\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__number\" data-name=\"Chamomile\"></div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"ariya-ing-card__name\">Chamomile Extract 10:1</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__spec\">1.2% apigenin</span>\n          <p class=\"ariya-ing-card__purpose\">Encourages relaxation and helps the body wind down. Apigenin is the key flavonoid responsible for chamomile's calming effects.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-wrap\">\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage\">150</span>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-unit\">mg</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-card\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__number\" data-name=\"Tart Cherry\"></div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"ariya-ing-card__name\">Tart Cherry Extract 10:1</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__spec\">&ge;2% anthocyanins</span>\n          <p class=\"ariya-ing-card__purpose\">Provides naturally occurring compounds that support sleep and recovery. Anthocyanins are the active pigments verified in each batch.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-wrap\">\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage\">145</span>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-unit\">mg</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-card\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__number\" data-name=\"Magnolia Bark\"></div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"ariya-ing-card__name\">Magnolia Bark Extract</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__spec\">5% magnolol + honokiol &bull; HPLC verified</span>\n          <p class=\"ariya-ing-card__purpose\">Calms the nervous system and reduces nighttime stress. Magnolol and honokiol are dual bioactives confirmed via HPLC testing.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-wrap\">\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage\">60</span>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-unit\">mg</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-card\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__number\" data-name=\"Vitamin B6\"></div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__body\">\n          <h3 class=\"ariya-ing-card__name\">Vitamin B6</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__spec\">Pyridoxine HCl</span>\n          <p class=\"ariya-ing-card__purpose\">Supports neurotransmitter production involved in mood and sleep regulation.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-wrap\">\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage\">1</span>\n          <span class=\"ariya-ing-card__dosage-unit\">mg</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <hr class=\"ariya-ing-divider\">\n\n    <div class=\"ariya-ing-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"ariya-ing-section__heading\">Why Extract Ratios Matter</h2>\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-section__body\">Not every part of a plant contains the compounds responsible for its benefits. Extracts allow us to concentrate those naturally active compounds so every serving delivers reliable potency.</p>\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-section__body\">When you see ratios like 5:1 or 10:1, it means multiple parts of the raw plant were used to create a more concentrated extract.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"ariya-ing-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"ariya-ing-section__heading\">Why We Use Plant Extracts</h2>\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-section__body\">Each plant contains naturally occurring compounds that produce its benefits. We extract and concentrate those compounds so every bottle of Calm Nights works exactly as intended.</p>\n      <ul class=\"ariya-ing-section__list\">\n        <li>Lemon Balm contains <strong>Rosmarinic Acid</strong></li>\n        <li>Chamomile contains <strong>Apigenin</strong></li>\n        <li>Tart Cherry contains <strong>Anthocyanins</strong></li>\n        <li>Magnolia Bark contains <strong>Magnolol &amp; Honokiol</strong></li>\n      </ul>\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-section__body\" style=\"margin-top:20px;\">The plant is the source. The compound is what actually works. We build every batch around that, so there's no guessing.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <hr class=\"ariya-ing-divider\">\n\n    <div class=\"ariya-ing-section\">\n      <h2 class=\"ariya-ing-section__heading\">Clean Formula</h2>\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Non-GMO ingredients</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Vegan</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> No artificial colors</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> No added preservatives</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Potency tested</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Purity tested</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> GMP-compliant facility</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> FDA-registered facility</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Made in USA</div>\n        <div class=\"ariya-ing-clean-item\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Standardized extracts</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"ariya-ing-testing\">\n      <h2 class=\"ariya-ing-testing__heading\">Tested for Safety &amp; Quality</h2>\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-testing__body\">Every batch undergoes testing before release to verify purity, potency, and safety standards. Manufactured in Hauppauge, New York, USA.</p>\n      <div class=\"ariya-ing-testing__checks\">\n        <span class=\"ariya-ing-testing__check\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Heavy metals</span>\n        <span class=\"ariya-ing-testing__check\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Microbial contamination</span>\n        <span class=\"ariya-ing-testing__check\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><path d=\"M20 6L9 17l-5-5\"/></svg> Pesticide residues</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"ariya-ing-closing\">\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-closing__text\">You looked this up for a reason. We want you to feel confident in what you're putting in your body. This page exists because transparency isn't a luxury &mdash; it's a requirement.</p>\n      <p class=\"ariya-ing-closing__tagline\">60 capsules &bull; 30 servings &bull; $44.99</p>\n      <a href=\"/products/calm-nights\" class=\"ariya-ing-cta\">Shop Calm Nights</a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
